org.apache.catalina.startup

类 SimpleHttpClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.catalina.startup.SimpleHttpClient

  • public abstract class SimpleHttpClient
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple client for unit testing. It isn't robust, it isn't secure and should not be used as the basis for production code. Its only purpose is to do the bare minimum for the unit tests.

      • getResponseBodyUriElements

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> getResponseBodyUriElements()
        Return opening tags of HTML elements that were extracted by the extractUriElements() method.

        Note, that extractUriElements() method has to be called explicitly.

        返回:
        List of HTML tags, accumulated by extractUriElements() method, or null if the method has not been called yet.

      • extractUriElements

        public void extractUriElements()
        Scan the response body for opening tags of certain HTML elements (<a>, <form>). If any are found, then accumulate them.

        Note: This method has the following limitations: a) It assumes that the response is HTML. b) It searches for lowercase tags only.

        另请参阅:
        getResponseBodyUriElements()
